snippet: Ross Fisher opened the 2015 European Tour season with a six-under-par 66 to lead the Nedbank Golf Challenge in Sun City, South Africa.
abstract: Ross Fisher leads Nedbank Golf Challenge, opener of the 2015 European Tour season.
